Ifoni yakho ayixhunyiwe kwinsizakalo yedatha yefoni. Ukubuka lokhu kwaziswa manje, iya ku-%s kusiphequluli sewebhu.
Uma uke wasekela ngokulondoloza izilungiselelo zakho, zizobuyiselwa esimweni.
Izilungiselelo zakho ngeke zibuyiselwe ekusekeleni ngokulondoloza.
"Amaseva enkampani yakho zithumela ulwazi lokungena ngemvume efonini yakho. Lokhu kungathatha amaminithi ambalwa. Ikhasi lokungena ngemvume lenkampani yakho lizovela uma lokhu sekuqedile."
Lesi sizinda asisebenzisi Izinhlelo Zokusebenza ze-Google. Sicela uhlole igama lesizinda bese uzama futhi.

Ungasebenzisa i-akhawunti yakho ye-Google ukuze ulondoloze eceleni izinhlelo zokusebenza zakho, izilungiselelo (njenga mabhukimakhi nama phasiwedi okuxhuma kungenazintambo), nenye idatha. Uma wake walondoloza eceleni le-akhawunti, ungayibuyisela kule divayisi manje.
Gcina ledivayisi ilondiwe eceleni ne-Akhawunti ye-Google yami
Ngokuqhubeka, uvumela Izinqubomgomo Zobumfihlo Ezengeziwe kanye neze-Google.

ThintaQalisa" ukuze uqalise isevisi yakho yeselula manje. (Kungatha amaminithi ambalwa.)
Noma thinta "Yeqa ukuze uhlele ifoni yakho usebenzisa inethiwekhi Yokuxhumana kokungenantambo.
Thinta Yenza Kusebenze ukwenza kusebenze insizakalo yakho yefoni manje. (Kungase kuthathe amaminithi ambalwa.)

"Ngaphambili kokuthi wenze kusebenze, izinto eziningi eziqukethwe ucingo lwakho ngeke zisebenze.
Uma uncamela ukweqa manje, ungenza kusebenze esikhathini esizayo Ezisethweni."
Thinta Yeqa ukuze uqede ukuhlela usebenzisa uxhumano lwe-WiFi
Ukuqalisa kungathatha amaminithi ambalwa. Thinta Yeqa ukuqeda ukuhlela usebenzisa uxhumano lwe-WiFI.
Idivayisi yakho kumelwe iqalise ukuze kuqedelwe ukuvuselela.

Thinta Okulandelayo" ukuze uqhubeke.
Ukuqalisa kuphumelele, Kodwa kungathatha amaminithi ambalwa ukuze inethiwekhi yedatha yamaselula itholakale."

"Isevisi yakho yeselula ayisebenzisekanga. Lokhu kungaba inkinga yesikhashana.
Uma uncamela ukweqa manje, qinisekisa ukuthi ukwenza kusebenze ngesikhathi esizayo Kuzilungiselelo. Ngaphambili kokuthi wenze kusebenze, izinto eziningi eziqukethwe ifoni yakho ngeke zisebenze."
Isevisi yedata yeselula yakho ayikwazanga ukuthi yenziwe ukuthi isebenze. Lokhu kungaba inkinga yesikhashana kanti kungaxazululwa ngokuthi ucishe uphinde uvule ifoni yakho.

Ayikwazi ukuqalisa isevisi yedatha yamaselula. Ukuze uzame ukuqalisa futhi thinta Zama futhi".
Ungasebenzisa isevisi yedatha yamaselula akho kamuva Kuzilungiselelo ngaphansi "Kungenazintambo Namanethiwekhi Angenantambo amaselula
Ikhansela ukwenza kusebenze... lokhu kungase kuthathe amasekhondi angu-5-10.

Uqinisekile ufuna ukukhansela ukuqalisa? Kufanele uqalise isevisi yenethiwekhi yeselula ngaphambi kokuba ungayisebenzisa ukuze uxhume ku-Intanethi. Ukuze uzame ukuqalisa futhi cindezela Emuva".
Thitnta"Okulandelayo" ukuze uqede uhlelo usebenzisa inethiwekhi ye-WiFi.
Ungaqalisa isevisi inethiwekhi yeselula kamuva Kuzilungiselelo ngaphansi " Kungenazintambo uxhumano Namanethiwekhi amaselula

"Ukuqalisa kukhanseliwe.
Ungaqalisa insizakalo yedatha yeselula yakho kamuva Kuzilungiselelo ngaphansi"Kokungenantambo Namanethiwekhi amaselula.

Iphutha livelelile elidinga ukuvala shaqa nokuqalisa phansi ifoni yakho ngaphambi kokuba kwenziwe omunye umzamo wokwenza kusebenze. Ifoni yakho izovala shaqa ngokuzenzakalelayo emasekhondini angu-60, noma ungathinta Vala shaqa manje".
Emva kokuba ithebhulethi yakho ivale shaqa, cindezela inkinobho yayo Yamandla ukuyiqalisa phansi."
Thinta lana ukusebenzisa futhi Iseluleki Sokumisa
Ucingo lusebenzisa igama lakho ukwenza ukuthi ezinye izinsiza zifanele wena.

"Isevisi yendawo yakwa-Google isebenzisa i-data eqhamuka emithonjeni efana namanethiwekhi e-Wi-Fi ukusiza izinsiza zihlonze ukuthi cishe ukephi nendawo ngisho ngabe i-GPS ayitholakali.
Ungakushintsha lokhu okukhethwayo Ezinsizeni nganoma isiphi isikhathi."

Vumela isevisi yendawo yakwa-Google ukuthi iqoqe ulwazi olungaqondene namuntu olumayelana nendawo Eminye yemininingwane ingagcineka edivayisini yakho. Ukuqoqa kungnzeka ngisho noma ingekho insiza esebnzayo.
Sebenzisa Indawo Yami yemiphumela Yokusesha nge-Google namanye amasevisi e-Google.

"Uyavuma ukuthi ifoni yakho ingemukela iphinde ifake izibuyekezo ezivela ku-Google..
Ukusebenzisa kwakho le foni kungaphansi kwezinqubomgomo zobumfihlo neminye imigom yokusetshenziswa. "Funda kabanzi
Ifoni yakho ilungiselelwe ukusebenza futhi ikulungele ukusetshenziswa.
Qala i-Verizon Backup Assistant ukubuyisa oxhumana nabo kusuka kolunye ucingo le-Verizon.

Ungathanda ukusetha insizakalo yedatha engenantambo? Kulenyanga, isevisi yokukhokha njengoba uhamba inezinketho ezifanelo zonke izindlela zokuphila. Uma ungakwenzi, ungakwenza kamuva kusuka kumenye Yezilungiselelo.
